1. *Ruža* je najlepši cvet u mom vrtu. (Rose is the most beautiful flower in my garden.)
2. Kupila sam *roznu* boju za zidove. (I bought a rosy color for the walls.)
3. *Ružama* smo ukrasili sto za večeru. (We decorated the dinner table with roses.)
4. Videla sam *ružan* film sinoć. (I saw an ugly movie last night.)
5. *Ružnoća* nije u fizičkom izgledu, već u karakteru. (Ugliness is not in physical appearance, but in character.)
6. Kupila sam *ružičasti* džemper u radnji. (I bought a pink sweater at the store.)
7. *Ružno* ponašanje nije dozvoljeno u ovom restoranu. (Bad behavior is not allowed in this restaurant.)
8. Neki ljudi ne vole *ruže* zbog njihovog mirisa. (Some people don't like roses because of their scent.)
9. Stavila sam *ruž* na usne pre nego što sam izašla. (I put on lipstick before I went out.)
10. Pokušala sam da *uzgojim* svoje ruže u vrtu, ali nisu uspele. (I tried to grow my own roses in the garden, but they didn't succeed.)